text: Ventseslav Kanchev (born 9 December 1953) is a Bulgarian rowing coxswain. He competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Plovdiv Category:Coxswains (rowing)
